        },
        "subject": "LU-19584 lraft: var declarations in the middle of functions",
        "message": "LU-19584 lraft: var declarations in the middle of functions\n\nThe lraft is imported as-is from another repo. There are\nvariable declarations in the middle of functions. It would\nbe possible to fix these errors in our copy of this code,\nbut it would be better to disable the\n`-Werror=declaration-after-statement` warning when building\nthis module, so that we don't need to edit the repo every\ntime it is updated from upstream.\n\nAlso include random.h for get_random_int()\n\nFixes: 65093581cc (\"EX-12009 lraft: port raft to kernel\")\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Artem Blagodarenko <ablagodarenko@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: I05f9a3eaed2aafed7e39096c8c2fe64665938ffe\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
